7.description:
```javascript
const arr = ['pool', 'loud', 'slow', 'sour'];
let count = 0;
const s = 'o';
for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++){
  for (let j = 0; j < arr[i].length; j++) {
    if (arr[i][j] === s) {
      count++;
    }
  }
}
console.log(count);
```

